New Records: Brice Sensabaugh scored 27 points and made 5 out of 6 three-pointers in the Jazz's win.

The Magic struggled with a 36% shooting performance and missed several key players.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played at the Kia Center in Orlando, Florida.
